@node ALTAR "Altar of Dementia"

@{b}Altar of Dementia@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 2
Artist  = Brom

Text(TP): Sacrifice a creature: Target player puts a
          number of cards equal to that creature's power
          from the top of his or her library into his or
          her graveyard.

Flavor Text: @{i}"It is not that you will go mad. It is that you will
              beg for madness." ---Volrath@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode

@node BOOBY "Booby Trap"

@{b}Booby Trap@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 6
Artist  = Doug Chaffee

Text(TP): When Booby Trap comes into play, name a card
          other than a basic land. Whenever target
          opponent draws any cards, he or she reveals those
          cards to all players. If any of those cards is
          the named card, Sacrifice Booby Trap and it deals
          10 damage to that player.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BOOBY}

@endnode
@node BOTTL "Bottle Gnomes"

@{b}Bottle Gnomes@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(U)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 3
Artist  = Kaja Foglio

Text(TP): Sacrifice Bottle Gnomes: Gain 3 life.

Flavor Text: @{i}"I am reminded of the fable of the silver ef. Its owner
               cracks it open to see what jewels it holds, only to discover
               a simple yellow yolk." ---Karn, silver golem@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
