@{b}Coiled Tinviper@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(C)
Type    = Artifact Creature (2/1)
Cost    = 3
Artist  = John Matson

Text(TP): First strike

Flavor Text: @{i}The bite of the tinviper feels most like a razor draws
               across the tongue.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node COLD_ "Cold Storage"

@{b}Cold Storage@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Greg Simanson

Text(TP): <3>: Put target creature you control on Cold Storage.
