@node CURSE "Cursed Scroll"

@{b}Cursed Scroll@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 1
Artist  = D. Alexander Gregory

Text(TP): <3T>: Name a card. Target opponent chooses
          a card at random from your hand. If he or she
          chooses the named card, Cursed Scroll deals 2
          damage to target creature or player.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/CURSC}

@endnode
@node ECHO_ "Echo Chamber"

@{b}Echo Chamber@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Donato Giancola

Text(TP): <4T>: Target opponent chooses target creature
          he or she controls. Put a token creature into
          play and treat it as a copy of that creature.
          The token creature is unaffected by summoning
          sickness this turn. At end of turn, remove the
          token creature from the game. Play this ability
          as a sorcery.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_E.guide/ECHO_}

@endnode
