@node MAGNE "Magnetic Web"

@{b}Magnetic Web@{ub}

Color   = Artifact
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 2
Artist  = Adam Rex

Text(TP): If any creature with any magnet counters on it
          attacks, all creatures with magnet counters on
          them that the attacking player controls attack
          if able. If any creature with any magnet counters
          on it attacks, all creatures with magnet counters
          on them that the defending player controls block
          that creature if able.
          <1T>: Put a magnet counter on target creature.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_M.guide/MAGWE}

